sentences.english: A little down? Do you mean move it down to the left?
sentences.chinese: 有点往下？你的意思是说把它往左边移下一点。

sentences.english: My mouse cursor is over here on the top right, now, I touch the cat.
sentences.chinese: 我们鼠标移到右上方时，我们摸了下猫。

sentences.english: He ordered all the port cannon to be heaved to starboard to counteract the list.
sentences.chinese: 他命令把左弦上所有的大炮移到右舷以抵消船的倾斜。

sentences.english: Depress switch mounting tabs to remove switch from bezel.
sentences.chinese: 降低开关装置设定，以从玻璃框移去开关。

sentences.english: Then May comes, and herders move up from the valleys to mountain pastures called jailoos.
sentences.chinese: 五月一到，牧人从山谷移到高山草原。

sentences.english: The new financial director, Mr. A moved his office up-stairs.
sentences.chinese: 新的财务主任A先生，把他的办公室移到楼上。

sentences.english: Using the sketch, it is now possible to tabulate the coordinates of all the nodes .
sentences.chinese: 应用草图，现在可以将所有结点的坐标移制成表。

sentences.english: Jackson's triumph in 1828 changed the emphasis to warrior presidents .
sentences.chinese: 1828年杰克逊的当选把重点移到能征善战的总统。

sentences.english: As you exhale, rock your pelvis forward and release.
sentences.chinese: 而当你呼气时，将盆骨往前移同时放松肌肉。

sentences.english: When the shear line vapour band is weak, and the Plateau shear line will move southeastward.
sentences.chinese: 切变线水汽带减弱时，高原切变线东南移。

sentences.english: The mathematical transformation is fixed and the airfoil is moved to generate different airfoil geometries .
sentences.chinese: 数学变换是固定机翼的翼型几何移到产生不同。

sentences.english: She anglicised her name after moving from Paris to London.
sentences.chinese: 从巴黎移到伦敦后，她使自己的名字英国化了。

sentences.english: However, by the time he had shifted his body the doe had vanished.
sentences.chinese: 然而，这时雌鹿消失了，他移了移身子。

sentences.english: Run additional commands for each of your assemblies that should be removed from the GAC…
sentences.chinese: 运行其它需要移徐出GAC程序集的命令。

sentences.english: As I bent down, he moved weakly toward me.
sentences.chinese: 我弯下腰去，它很虚弱地朝我移了过来。

sentences.english: We will cut the buck and insist on advancing along our set goal.
sentences.chinese: 我们将不负重望，坚持不移按着既定目标，走下去。
